==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Axillary
<hw>Ax"il*la*ry</hw> <pr>(⟦acr⟧ks"⟦icr⟧l*l⟦asl⟧*r⟦ycr⟧)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Axil</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>Of or pertaining to the axilla or armpit;
<as>as, <ex>axillary</ex> gland, artery, nerve</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Situated in, or rising from, an
axil; of or pertaining to an axil.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Axillary</xex>
buds.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Gray.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Axinite</ent>⟦br⟧
